Class DeliveryInfos

  • java.lang.Object
    • DeliveryInfos

  • public class DeliveryInfos
extends java.lang.Object
    The class DeliveryInfos represents the Delivery Information of the application. It contains an ArrayList of all the deliveries transacted.

      • showDelivery

        public java.lang.String showDelivery(java.lang.String t)
        Returns the information of the specific Delivery whose tracking information matches the input. If the input does not match to any delivery, the message "Does not Exist!" is returned instead.
        Parameters:
        t - Tracking Number which will be used to find the delivery.
        Returns:
        String information of the matching delivery. Returns "Does not Exist" instead if the input does not match any delivery.
